                    "sentence_id": "10",
                    "paragraph_index": 4,
                    "global_sentence_index": 24
                },
                {
                    "sentence": "Mitchell reported to Thomas and took command of the detached XIV Corps during the Battle of Nashville and the subsequent pursuit of the retreating Confederate army of John Bell Hood",
